AI Group Online Output Processing Testmod
==========================================

This testmod exercises the online output processing capabilities added
for AI/ML training data generation (ACE, Samudra) across all active
E3SM components:

EAM:  Vertical coarsening (pressure layers), derived fields, FLUS/FSUS/DTENDTTW
ELM:  Vertical coarsening (soil depth layers), derived soil water fields
MPAS-O: ACE depth coarsening and derived fields (SST/SSS) analysis members
MPAS-SI: ACE sea ice derived fields analysis member

Horizontal remapping is not exercised here (requires map files).
Set horiz_remap_file / hist_horiz_remap_file in user_nl_* to test.

Test: SMS_D_Ln5.ne4pg2_r05_oQU480.WCYCL1850NS.allactive-aigroup_output
